de an explanation for\nhot supra-arcade plasma sheets that are often observed in X-rays and extreme\nultraviolet wavelengths during the decay phase of large flares.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Oct 2019 19:52:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
