 20 frames per second with comparable detection\nresults to the state-of-the-art, achieving a 2 times speedup.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 12 Oct 2019 04:06:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2020 23:59:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 25 May 2023 02:56:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
