r rate and its measure of uncertainty is a full\nBayesian approach, which leads to a reasonable improvement over the direct\ncoverage error rate in terms of mean squared error (MSE) and confidence\ninterval (CI) as provided by the U.S. Census Bureau.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 12 Oct 2019 05:05:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-15"}
