 the Whole Correct Ratio(WCR)(%) with respect to\nimages as 71.39, and the Average Error Ratio(AER)(%) with respect to\nchromosomes as about 1.17.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 12 Oct 2019 13:36:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 28 Jun 2020 07:05:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 4 Jul 2020 23:12:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 8 Jul 2020 12:30:57 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 19 Jul 2020 12:51:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-21"}
